  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together chimichurri, brown sugar, salt, and black pepper.",
    "3. Add chicken to the bowl and toss to coat with marinade.",
    "4. Thread marinated chicken onto skewers.",
    "5. Brush grill grates with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "6. Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until chicken is cooked through.",
    "7. Transfer skewers to a plate and sprinkle with parsley.",
    "8. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
